Yes, I'm reffering to rows in a tracker. Usually it is 2-8 frames per row. 6 is default by tradition, it is 125 BPM for PAL. Usually it is 16-32 rows per measure, depending from the minimal note length you want to have.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=4205">Shiru</a> — Fri Nov 18, 2011 12:28 pm</p><hr />
